                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">2024 年野生动物保护（修订）条例于 8 月 1 日正式生效，将野鸽列入禁止喂饲野生动物的规定，提高了最高刑罚罚款和引入了定额罚款机制。渔护署高级动物护理主任石仲堂指狮子山公园安装的闭路电视目前已经成功检控 6 宗喂饲猴子的个案，正计划在更多地方增设闭路电视。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254533" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mfile_1764114_1_2024-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mfile_1764114_1_2024-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/mfile_1764114_1_2024.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1747568-20240405.htm">RTHK</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">狮子山公园安装的闭路电视装有人工智能系统，能有效辨认人类和猴子同时出现的时段并分析出最大机会有人喂饲的时间。他指目前已于喂饲野生动物的黑点安装红外线相机记录喂饲时间和频率，正考虑为执法人员增配随身相机等装置协助执法行动。修例后将由食环署、康文署及房屋署人员就非法喂饲野生动物执法，渔护署亦会加强巡查黑点，有需要时会联合行动。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254535 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240215_110320_0-e1722590288451-459x580.jpg" alt="" width="459" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240215_110320_0-e1722590288451-459x580.jpg 459w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/20240215_110320_0-e1722590288451.jpg 712w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 459px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254536 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dnsj0405h7n9004-e1722590312600-694x426.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="426" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dnsj0405h7n9004-e1722590312600-694x426.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dnsj0405h7n9004-e1722590312600.jpg 967w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">图片来源：<a href="https://www.singtaousa.com/2024-07-31/%e7%a6%81%e9%a4%b5%e9%87%8e%e9%b4%bf%e4%bf%ae%e8%a8%82%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b8-1%e5%af%a6%e6%96%bd-%e9%a6%96%e6%9c%88%e5%85%88%e4%bd%9c%e5%8f%a3%e9%a0%ad%e8%ad%a6%e5%91%8a9-1%e5%8d%b3%e6%99%82%e5%9f%b7/4944430#page4">星岛</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">立法会议员李世荣相信修例后提高的刑罚具足够阻吓力，建议当局加强宣传提醒外国旅客切勿违法。他认为目前有足够的执法人员，但目前闭路电视等装置覆盖率未够高令搜证有一定的困难，建议加强应用科技协助搜证。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20240802/s00001/1722569153185/%E7%A6%81%E9%A4%B5%E9%87%8E%E9%B4%BF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E7%94%9F%E6%95%88-%E6%BC%81%E8%AD%B7%E7%BD%B2%E7%A0%94%E5%A2%9E%E8%A8%AD%E9%96%89%E8%B7%AF%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%8A%A9%E6%90%9C%E8%AD%89?fbclid=IwY2xjawEZdMhleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHf2dPChWK4bNmZJo8t8dE8Gud0QXHQ421lqlFYYpOHxxAp4ki4Yuq4wz7w_aem_kcejvlb9ikrkgHvPD4Zwug">明报</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1764114-20240731.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/26/hkgov-cctv-2000-2500/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">邓炳强拟为 CCTV 引入人脸识别，加装 CCTV 计划或由 2000 添至 2500 部</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/27/security-bureau-plan-to-set-up-2000-cctv-in-hk-each-year/tech-secure/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">保安局拟每年全港安装 2000 部 CCTV　邓炳强：情况允许或会再增设数目</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/02/territory-wide-feeding-ban/life-tech/smartcity/">渔护署拟增设闭路电视协助执法　成功检控 6 宗喂饲猴子个案</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
